						<IMG src="http://www.archspace.org/image/forum/posticon.gif" border=0> posted 2005-03-23 09:39&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;
 						<A href="edit.php?board=sug&id=2189"><IMG alt="Edit/Delete Message" src="http://www.archspace.org/image/forum/edit.gif" border=0></A> 
